overview: Rohit and Sunaina once a happily married couple now have bitterness in their relationship, Rohit desperately needs a baby, but Sunaina is unable to fulfil his desire. Soon when Prerna , Sunaina’s sister enters their life, Rohit thinks of a plan to fulfill his wish , will his plan be successful or backfired, watch this series to find out.
title: Sunheri Yaadein
